{"tid":1540653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Do you hear the people sing 5 demands, not 1 less?","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:59:45.000Z","uid":306180,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4ccb222f15c7f2e7a6659f3a5364437207350eb0","tid":1540653,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"Dear fellow Hongkongers and friends from overseas,<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam is trying to fool us, once again. In the past few months, the HKSAR government has fully exposed their incompetence to rule the city and has been brutally violating fundamental rights of Hongkongers. Thousands are arrested and tortured. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Our tears and bloods shall not go in vain. 5 demands, not 1 less. <br />\nVictory is still yet to come. We carry on this fight!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#5DemandsNot1Less<br />\n#TooLittleTooLate<br />\n#FullDemocaryforHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04oFgvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04oFgvu.jpg&h=09a16da2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auVMb3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauVMb3Q.jpg&h=760f6516&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4xVPQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4xVPQx.jpg&h=3ac03613&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0decf86a504392f20742a5debfec45cc2b18d43","tid":1540653,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"要贏國際輿論就同我入嚟， 人哋根本唔知你哋啲口號up乜鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ea975ced0961248dbd1c4a3ce2d295cdf9230d9","tid":1540653,"uid":233982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/