E DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES."},{"pid":"cb8703853aeea9aea4ce7acf6623719756230306","tid":1540653,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"Carrie Lam is trying to fool us, once again."},{"pid":"20a6739abc25873bc315b06fb8c1a2cfba7c5ed2","tid":1540653,"uid":186782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"five demands not one less!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPlease push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6623baa1f15291517f43e6ac40d0ac7d1aee0f54","tid":1540653,"uid":128912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:50:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"146689c0c80dcf18fd46ddc6904343021a1dc434","tid":1540653,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"The bill is still not dead.<br />\nCarrie Lam lies to all the world<br />\nThe bill can be passed by the government"},{"pid":"26408f57f5dbdf37264a114876debad9827653f9","tid":1540653,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ccb222f15c7f2e7a6659f3a5364437207350eb0","tid":1540653,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"Dear fellow Hongkongers and friends from overseas,<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam is trying to fool us, once again. In the past few months, the HKSAR government has fully exposed their incompetence to rule the city and has been brutally violating fundamental rights of Hongkongers. Thousands are arrested and tortured. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Our tears and bloods shall not go in vain. 5 demands, not 1 less. <br />\nVictory is still yet to come. We carry on this fight!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#5DemandsNot1Less<br />\n#TooLittleTooLate<br />\n#FullDemocaryforHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04oFgvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04oFgvu.jpg&h=09a16da2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auVMb3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauVMb3Q.jpg&h=760f6516&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4xVPQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4xVPQx.jpg&h=3ac03613&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"Yeah! The extradition bill hasn't formally been withdrawn by vote in the legislative council .<br />\n<br />\nPlease keep fighting for our important demands ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5087cb2a2e033387caef46e49e5d616e84169d","tid":1540653,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9aba4eff5c498dfaf7e4ebaa7ee7fc7dd6b132a9","tid":1540653,"uid":129413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"標題有聲"},{"pid":"4a6f95d0029e9a571f8e5a78b939576449ddedfb","tid":1540653,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/